menu "Power Management Configuration"

config POWER_INACTIVITY_TIMEOUT_MS
    int "Inactivity Timeout (milliseconds)"
    default 300000
    range 10000 3600000
    help
        Time in milliseconds before entering deep sleep when:
        - No BLE connections active
        - No rowing activity detected

        Default: 300000 ms (5 minutes)

        Recommended values:
        - 60000: 1 minute (aggressive power saving)
        - 300000: 5 minutes (balanced)
        - 600000: 10 minutes (conservative)

endmenu
